Garci, Oscar candidate in four nominations (of which he won one), is of the opinion and assured that none of the three candidates representing Spain in front of the Academy of Hollywood this year are a young generation of Spanish filmography. Neither `Sangre de mayo', nor `Site mesas de billar francés', nor finally the selected movie `Los girasoles ciegos'.
